---
import { ArrowRight, MessageCircle } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section class="relative py-32 px-6 overflow-hidden">
  
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-background">
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-150 h-100 bg-brand-cyan-dark/20 blur-[100px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern opacity-20 pointer-events-none"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight">
      ¿LISTO PARA TOMAR EL <span class="text-gradient">CONTROL?</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      La infraestructura ya está montada y los nodos activos. <br class="hidden md:block"/>
      Crea tu cuenta ahora y despliega tu servidor en segundos.
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
      
      <a href="https://panel.arkaniahost.com" class="btn-primary group">
        Crear Servidor
        <ArrowRight size={18} class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
      </a>

      <a href="https://discord.gg/arkania" target="_blank" class="px-6 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-white border border-white/10 hover:bg-white/5 hover:border-brand-magenta/50 hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 flex items-center gap-2">
        <MessageCircle size={18} />
        Unirse a Discord
      </a>

    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-slate-500 font-mono">
      Sin tarjetas de crédito • Cancelación en cualquier momento
    </p>

  </div>
</section>